import React from 'react';
import './scss/Blog.scss'

import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-grid-system';


export const Blog = () => {
    return <Container>
    <Row>
        <Col sm={4}>
            One of three columns
    </Col>
        <Col sm={4}>
            One of three columns
    </Col>
        <Col sm={4}>
            One of three columns
    </Col>
    </Row>
</Container>
}
